174 A.3d 509 JACQUELINE JALIL, LUISA ROJAS, AND TANIA MENA, PLAINTIFFS-RESPONDENTS, v. PILGRIM MEDICAL CENTER AND DR. NICHOLAS CAMPANELLA, DEFENDANTS-PETITIONERS.

C-142 September Term 2017

079512 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002906-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
